# Homework Week 4

Base your week 4 homework on the result of week 3.

## Outline

Refactor your todo list app so that all state is handled by Redux stores. You _may_ want to keep some form state as local state inside React components. But think carefully about this.

Make sure to only mutate your store(s) with Redux actions --> reducers.

Make a full CRUD (Create Read Update Delete) Todo flow